div.p:
Frequent Sailings from ALEXANDRIA to LIVERPOOL, also Regular Services
                            from LIVERPOOL to ALEXANDRIA and to ALGERIA, MALTA, LEVANT, BLACK SEA,
                            and other Mediterranean Ports.

Mr. J.D. White asked the secratary for Foreign Affairs whether the hanging
                        and flogging of natives at Danishwai on June28 were of a public character;
                        whether some hundreds of natives, men and women, were present as spectators;
                        and, if so, whether steps would be taken to have the execution of any such
                        sentences in Egypt conducted in accordance with the usage of civilised
                        nations.
